Please follow these instructions:

  • Ensure your scan file/s are in .stl format only
  • Your files should not be more than 64mb in size
  • Fill out all the required fields
  • Give us as much information about this case to avoid delays.
  • Once we receive your file we will manually check it
  • If there are any issues, we will promptly get in touch

All work is turned around in 5 days from receipt of scan files (before 11am). Express turnaround is available.

If you would like to discuss anything with the digital team, please email digital@costech.co.uk or call us on 01474 320076.
